**Monk** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous | Haunted
__Basics__
The Monk will survive the first attempt to banish it during the night.
__Details__
The Monk is informed of the attempt to banish them.
Attempts to banish the Monk during the day will still succeed.

__Simplified__
The Monk will survive the first attempt to banish it. They will learn when the protection is used.

__Formalized__
Haunted Role
Starting: Protect @Self from `Banishments` through Passive Defense during Night (~UntilUse)
On Passive Defense: Learn `Defense Used`

__Card__
With strong spiritual power, the Monk can resist being banished.
